00214 void rna_Modifier_name_set(PointerRNA *ptr, const char *value)
00215 {
00216     ModifierData *md = ptr->data;
00217     char oldname[sizeof(md->name)];
00218     
00219     /* make a copy of the old name first */
00220     BLI_strncpy(oldname, md->name, sizeof(md->name));
00221     
00222     /* copy the new name into the name slot */
00223     BLI_strncpy_utf8(md->name, value, sizeof(md->name));
00224     
00225     /* make sure the name is truly unique */
00226     if (ptr->id.data) {
00227         Object *ob = ptr->id.data;
00228         modifier_unique_name(&ob->modifiers, md);
00229     }
00230     
00231     /* fix all the animation data which may link to this */
00232     BKE_all_animdata_fix_paths_rename(NULL, "modifiers", oldname, md->name);
00233 }

00252 static void rna_Smoke_set_type(Main *bmain, Scene *scene, PointerRNA *ptr)
00253 {
00254     SmokeModifierData *smd = (SmokeModifierData *)ptr->data;
00255     Object *ob = (Object*)ptr->id.data;
00256     ParticleSystemModifierData *psmd = NULL;
00257     ParticleSystem *psys = NULL;
00258     ParticleSettings *part = NULL;
00259 
00260     /* nothing changed */
00261     if ((smd->type & MOD_SMOKE_TYPE_DOMAIN) && smd->domain)
00262         return;
00263         
00264     smokeModifier_free(smd); /* XXX TODO: completely free all 3 pointers */
00265     smokeModifier_createType(smd); /* create regarding of selected type */
00266 
00267     switch (smd->type) {
00268         case MOD_SMOKE_TYPE_DOMAIN:
00269             ob->dt = OB_WIRE;
00270             break;
00271         case MOD_SMOKE_TYPE_FLOW:
00272             for (psys = ob->particlesystem.first; psys; psys = psys->next)
00273                 if (psys->part->type == PART_EMITTER)
00274                     break;
00275             if (ob->type == OB_MESH && !psys) {
00276                 /* add particle system */
00277                 psmd = (ParticleSystemModifierData *)object_add_particle_system(scene, ob, NULL);
00278                 if (psmd) {
00279                     psys = psmd->psys;
00280                     part = psys->part;
00281                     part->lifetime = 1.0f;
00282                     part->sta = 1.0f;
00283                     part->end = 250.0f;
00284                     part->ren_as = PART_DRAW_NOT;
00285                     part->draw_as = PART_DRAW_DOT;
00286                     BLI_strncpy(psys->name, "SmokeParticles", sizeof(psys->name));
00287                     psys->recalc |= (PSYS_RECALC_RESET|PSYS_RECALC_PHYS);
00288                     DAG_id_tag_update(ptr->id.data, OB_RECALC_DATA);
00289                 }
00290             }
00291             if (smd->flow)
00292                 smd->flow->psys = psys;
00293         case MOD_SMOKE_TYPE_COLL:
00294         case 0:
00295         default:
00296             ob->dt = OB_TEXTURE;
00297             break;
00298     }
00299     
00300     /* update dependency since a domain - other type switch could have happened */
00301     rna_Modifier_dependency_update(bmain, scene, ptr);
00302 }
